---
title: Zesty Tilapia Tacos with Fresh DIY salsa
description: Easy as 1, 2, 3! These tilapia and Mexican-spiced tilapia tacos are dressed with DIY fresh salsa, zippy sour cream and perfectly-charred green peppers.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/zesty-tilapia-tacos-167dcc93-01d53714.jpg
